{"tid":2083826,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指美《自治法案》史上最辣 鍾國斌：企業憂撐惡法受制裁","createTime":"2020-06-29T04:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T06:34:25.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d3e4d469f9f1420d79adcf83c48fcb9916f34c42","tid":2083826,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:19:36.000Z","msg":"美國參議院香港時間上周五通過《香港自治法案》（Hong Kong Autonomy Act），是美國回應北京強立「港版國安法」的舉措。不過中國繼續審議這條惡法，傳聞將於7月1日正式實施。紡織及製衣界立法會議員鍾國斌今早接受電台訪問時表示，很多商會代表都支持法案，形容「99.9%」生意人都守規矩，不過他就指商界更擔心美國國會通過的《香港自治法案》，形容法案是「史上最辣」。<br />\n<br />\n外界盛傳「港版國安法」部份罪行刑罰最高會終身監禁，鍾國斌認為商界都不太擔心，而外資並無撤走，他指假如「港版國安法」立法後，街頭示威會減少，營商環境會更穩定。不過商界擔心美國國會通過的《香港自治法案》，擔心不知道表態支持港版國安法企業會否被制裁，但相信亞太區內可以取代香港經濟地位的選擇不多，對本港營商環境的影響有限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/K5IUSLG55ZZJ5BQQL3PDR7GJDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FK5IUSLG55ZZJ5BQQL3PDR7GJDM%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8ZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=4bfd9408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FK5IUSLG55ZZJ5BQQL3PDR7GJDM%2F&h=4495403b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/K5IUSLG55ZZJ5BQQL3PDR7GJDM/</a>"},{"pid":"6364dde386a80e097f1d4df831a95e505cfbe26f","tid":2083826,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEpj5kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEpj5kb.jpg&h=d66f7ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2KDBrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2KDBrX.jpg&h=a5c2a855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4w0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4w0k.jpg&h=82cb5faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決定前聽一聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/